      %h1 Resume Builder

      %p Enter your information below to build a PDF resume from your public Linkedin Profile. No data entered is saved.

      %p
        %small N.B. Not everything on LinkedIn is available on your public profile.

      %br

      %form{ "ng-submit" => "submitUsername()" }
        %label Enter your LinkedIn username
        %span.monospace http://linkedin.com/in/
        %input.inline.monospace{ type: 'text', "ng-model" => "username", placeholder: 'rowanhogan', "ng-style" => "{ 'width' : (username.length * .6) + 'em' }" }

        %button{ type: "submit", "ng-disabled" => "!username" } Start!

